    <title>markdown语法</title>
    <link href="/2021/02/27/markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/"/>
    <url>/2021/02/27/markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h1><p>markdown支持两种标题格式<br>1.使用=和-标记一级标题和二级标题</p><blockquote><p>格式:  </p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">一级标题<br>=======<br><br>二级标题<br>--------<br><span class="hljs-code">```  </span><br><span class="hljs-code"></span><br><span class="hljs-code">2.使用#号标记</span><br><span class="hljs-code">使用#号可表示1-6级标题</span><br><span class="hljs-code">格式:</span><br><span class="hljs-code">```markdown</span><br><span class="hljs-code"># 一级标题</span><br><span class="hljs-code">## 二级标题</span><br><span class="hljs-code">### 三级标题</span><br><span class="hljs-code">#### 四级标题</span><br><span class="hljs-code">##### 五级标题</span><br><span class="hljs-code">###### 六级标题</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><h1 id="段落格式"><a href="#段落格式" class="headerlink" title="段落格式"></a>段落格式</h1><p>markdown段落没有特殊的段落格式，可以直接书写，段落换行是两个以上空格加回车。也可以在段落后面使用一个空行，开始一个新的段落。<br>1.字体  </p><blockquote><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-emphasis">*斜体文本*</span><br><span class="hljs-emphasis">_斜体文本_</span><br><span class="hljs-strong">**粗体文本**</span><br><span class="hljs-strong">__粗体文本__</span><br><span class="hljs-strong">**<span class="hljs-emphasis">*粗斜体文本<span class="hljs-strong">**<span class="hljs-emphasis">*</span></span></span></span><br><span class="hljs-strong"><span class="hljs-emphasis"><span class="hljs-strong"><span class="hljs-emphasis"><span class="hljs-strong">__<span class="hljs-emphasis">_粗斜体文本<span class="hljs-strong">__<span class="hljs-emphasis">_</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.分割线<br>你可以在一行中用三个以上的星号、减号、底线来建立一个分隔线，行内不能有其他东西。你也可以在星号或是减号中间插入空格。下面每种写法都可以建立分隔线：  </p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-strong">**<span class="hljs-emphasis">*</span></span><br><span class="hljs-strong"><span class="hljs-emphasis"></span></span><br><span class="hljs-strong"><span class="hljs-emphasis">*</span> <span class="hljs-emphasis">* *</span></span><br><span class="hljs-strong"></span><br><span class="hljs-strong">**</span><span class="hljs-strong">**</span><br><span class="hljs-strong"></span><br><span class="hljs-strong">- - -</span><br><span class="hljs-strong"></span><br><span class="hljs-strong">------</span><br><span class="hljs-strong"></span><br><span class="hljs-strong">3.删除线  </span><br><span class="hljs-strong">```markdown</span><br><span class="hljs-strong">~~text~~</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p>4.下划线<br>下划线可以通过html的标签来实现</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">u</span>&gt;</span></span>text<span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">u</span>&gt;</span></span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p>5.脚注</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">[^要脚注的文本]<br>[<span class="hljs-symbol">^要脚注的文本</span>]:<span class="hljs-link">脚注内容</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><h1 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h1><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">无序列表<br><span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> text<br><br><span class="hljs-bullet">*</span> text<br><br><span class="hljs-bullet">+</span> text<br><br>有序列表<br>1.text<br>2.text<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p>还可以使用列表嵌套</p><h1 id="区块"><a href="#区块" class="headerlink" title="区块"></a>区块</h1><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-quote">&gt; text</span><br><span class="hljs-quote">&gt; text</span><br><span class="hljs-quote">&gt; text</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p>还可以有区块的嵌套，还可以在区块里使用列表等其他markdown语法。</p><h1 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h1><p>`printf(“hello world!”);`<br>代码片段</p><p>```javascript<br>$(document).ready(function () {<br>    alert(‘RUNOOB’);<br>});<br>```<br>代码区块</p><h1 id="链接"><a href="#链接" class="headerlink" title="链接"></a>链接</h1><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">[<span class="hljs-string">链接名称</span>](<span class="hljs-link">链接地址</span>)<br><br>或者<br><br>&lt;链接地址&gt;<br><br>高级链接<br>这个链接用 1 作为网址变量 [<span class="hljs-string">Google</span>][<span class="hljs-symbol">1</span>]<br>这个链接用 runoob 作为网址变量 [<span class="hljs-string">Runoob</span>][<span class="hljs-symbol">runoob</span>]<br>然后在文档的结尾为变量赋值（网址）<br><br>  [1]: http://www.google.com/<br>  [runoob]: http://www.runoob.com/<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a>图片</h1><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">![<span class="hljs-string">alt 属性文本</span>](<span class="hljs-link">图片地址</span>)<br><br>![<span class="hljs-string">alt 属性文本</span>](<span class="hljs-link">图片地址 &quot;可选标题&quot;</span>)<br><br>也可以像网址那样对图片网址使用变量<br><br>这个链接用 1 作为网址变量 [<span class="hljs-string">RUNOOB</span>][<span class="hljs-symbol">1</span>].<br>然后在文档的结尾为变量赋值（网址）<br><br>[<span class="hljs-symbol">1</span>]: <span class="hljs-link">http://static.runoob.com/images/runoob-logo.png</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h1><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">|  表头   | 表头  |<br>|  ----  | ----  |<br>| 单元格  | 单元格 |<br>| 单元格  | 单元格 |<br><br>-: 设置内容和标题栏居右对齐。<br>:- 设置内容和标题栏居左对齐。<br>:-: 设置内容和标题栏居中对齐。<br><br>| 左对齐 | 右对齐 | 居中对齐 |<br>| :-----| ----: | :----: |<br>| 单元格 | 单元格 | 单元格 |<br>| 单元格 | 单元格 | 单元格 |<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="高级技巧"><a href="#高级技巧" class="headerlink" title="高级技巧"></a>高级技巧</h1><ul><li>支持HTML元素</li><li>转义</li><li>公式</li></ul><h1 id="参考"><a href="#参考" class="headerlink" title="参考"></a>参考</h1><p>1.<a href="https://www.runoob.com/markdown/md-tutorial.html">菜鸟教程</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
